                            "bullet_points": "•  Includes 1 minifigure: Naboo pilot\r\n•  Features Naboo planet, Naboo starfighter mini-model and weapon\r\n•  Vehicle and minifigure display stand with plaque also included\r\n•  Hang your planet from the ceiling!\r\n•  Explore the LEGO® Star Wars galaxy while you play!\r\n•  Naboo planet diameter over 3” (9cm)\r\n•  Naboo Starfighter measures over 4” (12cm) long",
                            "display_title": "Naboo Starfighter™ & Naboo™",
                            "description": "Filled with swamps, grassy plains and vast underground oceans, Naboo plays an important role in Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace. Naboo deploys the sleek Naboo starfighter to defend itself against the clutches of the Trade Federation. Set includes an accurate model of Naboo, a Naboo pilot minifigure, a Naboo starfighter mini-model, a weapon and a display stand with name plaque. Collect the other Series 1 sets: 9675 Sebulba's Podracer & Tatooine and 9676 TIE Interceptor & Death Star!",
